{"tid":1415870,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「討論」點先可以令容易動搖嘅人支持我們地？","createTime":"2019-08-05T14:17:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T04:49:12.000Z","uid":71123,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"93c4a6d82d98e71ab3fa8c6301942f43e1d2b80d","tid":1415870,"uid":71123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:17:38.000Z","msg":"相信大家都留意到<br />\n總有啲人會喺手足做出超出佢地個框架嘅事嗰陣就會動搖 想割<br />\n<br />\n我就咁睇<br />\n香港人最大特點唔係善忘 而係極度受大環境影響而變得麻木<br />\n<br />\n2014年佔路比人屌到反皮 到而家佔路係min pay <br />\n6月班黑色強姦犯射tg rubber bullet大家驚到亂走 到今日好多手足都可以冷靜應對<br />\n甚至開始對黑狗強姦犯嘅所作所為麻木<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以 如果我地經常做啲對嗰班人黎講係過界嘅野 當然唔係一黎就殺狗 而係逐啲逐啲咁過界 等佢地習慣左之後就逐漸升級 好快佢地就會習慣手足所做嘅一切 然後就會覺得成件事係冇問題 <br />\n<br />\n如果好好利用呢個心態 我地就會少好多限制同反對聲音<br />\n<br />\n講到199 希望你地睇得明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n純討論 覺得我錯 請屌細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50919a935cf38e33191846de337f62cc51959966","tid":1415870,"uid":71123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:19:48.000Z","msg":"光"},{"pid":"c3386ba35397263b14f250b61b3af020d81b5d26","tid":1415870,"uid":71123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:20:10.000Z","msg":"復"},{"pid":"336fc5b38fddb8988ee9e12b2df4310483b8b922","tid":1415870,"uid":71123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:20:26.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"d577aebe40db5750ff465dd9ae57c5bd3e51fde9","tid":1415870,"uid":71123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:20:46.000Z","msg":"港"},{"pid":"007cf77564ecb4a6b90ade29e42865913aebff23","tid":1415870,"uid":71123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:21:00.000Z","msg":"時"},{"pid":"85c2b15756e7bca956eb3a82fc15004d4debb7a0","tid":1415870,"uid":71123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:21:13.000Z","msg":"代"},{"pid":